<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Hackathon Ada Lovelace</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 { color: #2c3e50; }
        p { color: #7f8c8d; }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Bem-vinda ao Hackathon!</h1>
        <p>Olá, <strong><%= nome %></strong>. Você está logado como <strong><%= tipo === 'ong' ? 'ONG' : 'Usuário' %></strong>.</p>
        <% if (user) { %>
            <a href="/logout" class="btn">Sair</a>
        <% } else { %>
            <a href="/login" class="btn">Entrar</a>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
